hondo717: |cp||at|An interesting hand. First of all, I like kia's 3@D bid which shows a strong 2 suiter, which is what he has. roberta with her A of hearts and K of diamonds should seriously consider bidding 4@H. This is a case where her hand goes up a great deal in value based on the bidding. If her ace and king were in the black suits, her hand is not nearly as valuable. Remember, honors in your partner's suit generally have more value than honors in the opponents suits. That is because honors work better when they are in combination with other honors.|
